library(cardinalR)
library(langevitour)
plane_2d_data <- plane(n = 300, coefficient_x_1 = 1, coefficient_x_2 = 1, coefficient_y_1 = -1, coefficient_y_2 = 1, intercept_x = -10, intercept_y = 8, 
u_min = 10, u_max = 30, v_min = 10, v_max = 20, num_noise = 2, 
min_n = 0, max_n = 1)

colnames(plane_2d_data) <- paste0("x", 1:NCOL(plane_2d_data))

langevitour(plane_2d_data, pointSize = 2)
